snippet: Odyssey Sims went 12 for 34 from the field but made up for it with seven rebounds and seven assists to go with her 44 points for the Lady Bears.
abstract: College Basketball Women's Roundup; Baylor beats Texas, 87-73; other women's scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Odyssey Sims went 12 for 34 from the field but made up for it with seven rebounds and seven assists to go with her 44 points for the Lady Bears.

headline.main: Off With Her Shot, Sims Still Scores 44 Points to Help Baylor Beat Texas
